description:

EACH Torrent will be as LARGE as it takes to seed a WHOLE letter of the Alphabet so this Part 1 includes all the numbers and the Letter A.

THIS IS ONLY THE TEXT FILE TELLING YOU WHAT THE CONTENTS OF THE PART 1 TORRENT ARE.

It is up to you to decide if you wish to commit your time and bandwidth to downloading the 16 GB plus monster of a download.

PLEASE DO NOT ATTEMPT TO JOIN THE MAIN TORRENT if you have poor download speeds!  You will just mess up the swarm and lower the average download speed.  This is NOT for those who do not know how to torrent.

Thank you.  Main torrent follows in a half hour or so.
